{
  "stem": "26609.13",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't know what they-- what ranks they had, in their shiny boots with helmets, armed, of course, two on the front, two on the side, and two at the back.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought of myself, whom are they guarding so-- They just guarded if someone would run away from this truck.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were-- It was the middle of winter, very cold, and there were naked children, you could see-- That's what I want from memory to paint, if I can do it-- you could see frozen, and hear screams.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because underneath it, all the children, they took out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't say exactly how many there were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There must have been about, in a big truck, about near 100, 80 or 90 children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Underneath, they were warm still, because the top was frozen, covered some of the children on top.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Underneath, they screamed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It must be terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Just-- one can't think of it, what deaths they had, alive all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you could see only stiff arms and legs, just-- they were one over the other, a heap, just quite a big heap of children, one over-- they threw them out, not thinking.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And some heads felling over on the edge, and other stiff, frozen necks hanging down, and arms on top.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just looked at it and I didn't know what I'm seeing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I felt faint, because I was on the path on one side, and there was-- on the other side in the center was that truck moving slowly.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I just felt-- I said, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "If you faint here-- so the police was everywhere around-- they will know that you are Jewish, so you can't faint.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Don't faint.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I feel that my knees got soft, that I'm going to fall.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
